<p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">据中国地震台网测定，北京时间</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">2022</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">6</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">月</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">1</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">日在四川省雅安市芦山县发生</span><em><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">M</span></em><sub><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">S</span></sub><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">6.1</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">地震；北京时间</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">2022</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">年</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">6</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">月</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">10</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">日在四川省阿坝州马尔康市发生</span><em><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">M</span></em><sub><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">S</span></sub><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">5.8/6.0</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">震群。昨天，北京广播电视台新闻广播某记者，围绕近期的四川地震话题，电话采访我，我做了简短的解答（已播出，见</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">20220610</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">期：新闻</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">2022</span><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">，有节选）。考虑到这些解答对大家了解地震有所帮助，我把其整理成文并分享之。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">Q1</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体;">、什么是震群型地震？它与普通的地震有什么区别？它的危害性是否更大？震群型地震 现在人们是否可以预防？</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">在一个较小范围内、较短时间内，发生的一连串关联地震统称为震群。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">震群是基本的地震活动方式，这是因为：某次地震发生后，震源破裂必然产生应力转移，其能引起震源周围岩石应力重分配，导致后续关联地震的发生。当然，如果应力转移量级较小而不满足后续地震的发生条件，或后续地震的震级太小，则只能观测到单个地震。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">在一个震群内，<span style="font-family: 宋体; text-indent: 32px;">通常</span>有一个较大事件或两个较大且震级接近的事件。此次</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: #222222; background: white;">马尔康震群有</span><em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">M</span></em><sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">S</span></sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif; color: #222222; background: white;">5.8/ 6.0</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: #222222; background: white;">两次较大事件，可称为双震震群。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: #222222; background: white; font-size: 16px;">无论单个地震还是震群，其危害性主要取决于震级和震源深度。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: #222222; background: white; font-size: 16px;">根据我们的研究，目前只有地震区的标志性地震可预测，因为其演化遵循确定性规律。标志性地震后的震群，其震级上限能预知。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif; color: #222222; background: white;">Q2</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体; color: #222222; background: white;">、据初步震源机制解显示，此次马尔康</span><em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">M</span></em><sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">S</span></sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif; color: #222222; background: white;">5.8/6.0</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体; color: #222222; background: white;">两次地震均为走滑型破裂，距松岗断裂最近，距离约</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif; color: #222222; background: white;">4</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体; color: #222222; background: white;">千米。什么是震源机制？走滑型破裂、距松岗断裂最近,应该如何理解？</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; background: white; font-size: 16px;">地震发生的物理过程称为震源机制，其可以通过多个地震台的地震记录图来确定。通过震源机制解，可求得破裂方向、破裂速度与应力降等参数。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; background: white;">走滑型破裂或地震，指发生在走滑型断裂上的地震，而走滑型断裂指两盘在力偶作用下作相对水平运动的断裂。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: #333333; background: white;">虽然这两次地震距</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; color: #222222; background: white;">松岗断裂最近，但是否发生在该断裂上，需要进一步研究，因为也可能发生在其他的隐伏断裂上。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">Q3</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体;">、四川马尔康地区有哪些地质特点，为什么这次这一地区附近发生了多次地震？</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">要理解地震，单独谈马尔康地区的地质和地震构造没有意义，得谈地震区，因为在同一个地震区内的断裂、地震都有内在关联，是一家。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">马尔康地区位于我们划定的汶川地震区(图<span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "times new roman";">1</span>)，位于同一个构造块体内；该地震区活动断裂发育、地震频发。我们的研究表明，由于</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">2008</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">年汶川</span><em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">M</span></em><sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">S</span></sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">8.1</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">地震仅为一次标志性地震而非主震，所以该地震区势必发生一系列的预震(是</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">preshock</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">，不是余震</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">aftershock</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">)和下一次标志性地震。汶川地震后，在该地震区发生了一系列的显著预震，如</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">2013</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">年芦山</span><em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">M</span></em><sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">S</span></sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">7.0</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">地震、</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">2017</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">年九寨沟</span><em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">M</span></em><sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">S</span></sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">7.0</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">地震、</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">2021</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">年玛多</span><em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">M</span></em><sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">S</span></sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">7.4</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">6.1</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">地震和马尔康</span><em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">M</span></em><sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">S</span></sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">5.8/6.0</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">地震。这些预震是有联系的，均属于第</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">3</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; background: white; overflow-wrap: break-word; text-align: start;">地震</span></strong></span><strong><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">）</span></strong></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">Q4</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 楷体;">、汶川地震后，貌似四川的地震活动更猛了，这是什么原因？</span><br></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">随时间延续，每个地震区的地震活动将呈现越来越猛的趋势，这是因为：随着锁固段按承载力由低到高次序的依次断裂，不断的荷载转移将导致剩余锁固段承受的荷载越来越大，故其破裂速率越来越快且破裂事件震级总体越来越大。</span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">以汶川地震区为例，在</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">1937</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">年玛多</span><em><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">M</span></em><sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">S</span></sub><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">7.8</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">级标志性地震前，地震活动较弱（</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">CBS</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">曲线平缓）；而之后，则越来越猛（</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">CBS</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">曲线陡增）。这说明该地震区的地震活动显著增强，并非始于</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">2008</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">年汶川地震，而是始于</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">1937</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">年玛多地震。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">2008</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">年汶川地震标志着第</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">2</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">锁固段已宏观断裂。由于如上所述的原因，目前第</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">3</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">锁固段破裂的地震活动会较之前更猛，这是符合力学原理的必然结果。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="font-size: 16px;"><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">与四川有密切关系的还有鲜水河、得荣、西昌地震区（图</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: "Times New Roman", serif;">3</span><span style="font-size: 16px; line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体;">），这些地震区的地震活动趋势与汶川地震区类似。</span></span></p><p style="text-indent:32px;line-height:200%"><span style="line-height: 200%; font-family: 宋体; font-size: 16px;">总之，四川的地震活动确实越来越猛了。</span></p><p style="line-height: 200%;
